      <title>现代斗争是抵抗被武器化的成瘾</title>
      <link>https://linguage.github.io/naval/zh/the-modern-struggle-is-fighting-weaponized-addiction.zh/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2020 16:46:00 +0000</pubDate>
